Description: Only src/vk_mem_alloc.h and LICENSE.txt files were imported.
Local Modifications: - added README.fuchsia
- line endings were auto-converted from CRLF
- indentation removed from blank newlines, trailing whitespace removed
- Thread annotation macros (__TA_*) added to compile with -Wthread-safety
- Clang formatting disabled
- suppress compilation warnings:
  -Wdeprecated-copy
  -Wmissing-field-initializers
  -Wnullability-completeness
  -Wunused-private-field
  -Wunused-variable
